data.description: Welcome to this charming 2-story home located in the neighborhood of Centennial Novak. You'll be captivated by the inviting ambiance, featuring tile floors and a spacious great room designed for entertaining. The heart of this home is its lovely kitchen, adorned with recessed lighting, rich chocolate-stained cabinets, and granite counters. You'll find ample storage with a pantry, and the center island doubles as a breakfast bar, perfect for casual meals. Sizable main bedroom offers a private retreat with its own bathroom, complete with dual sinks and a walk-in closet. A highlight of this property is the huge loft, providing an ideal space for creating your own entertainment area, whether it's for movie nights, games, or a cozy reading nook. Newly re-done backyard beckons with a serene atmosphere, featuring a paver seating area and plenty of space for outdoor activities and fun. A gem that promises not to disappoint. Don't miss the opportunity to come and experience it for yourself!
